#: ../../P/prowler.rst:5
msgid "prowler"
msgstr "prowler"

#: ../../P/prowler.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../P/prowler.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Unix] A :ref:`daemon` that is run periodically (typically once a week) to "
"seek out and erase :ref:`core` files, truncate administrative logfiles, nuke"
" :code:`lost+found` directories, and otherwise clean up the :ref:`cruft` "
"that tends to pile up in the corners of a file system. See also "
":ref:`reaper`\\, :ref:`skulker`\\."
msgstr ""
"[Unix]定期的に(典型的には週に一度)実行され、\\ :ref:`core`\\ ファイルを探し出して消去し、管理用ログファイルを切り詰め、\\ "
":code:`lost+found`\\ ディレクトリを一掃し、ファイルシステムの隅に溜まりがちな\\ :ref:`cruft`\\ を片付ける\\ "
":ref:`daemon`\\ 。\\ :ref:`reaper`\\ 、\\ :ref:`skulker`\\ も参照。"
